<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFW_E_Agar.2C_F_H_Drummond1948">W E Agar, F H Drummond (1948). "Third report on a test of McDougall's Lamarckian experiment on the training of rats". <i>Journal of Experimental Biology</i> <b>25</b>: 103.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Third+report+on+a+test+of+McDougall%27s+Lamarckian+experiment+on+the+training+of+rats&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Experimental+Biology&amp;rft.aulast=W+E+Agar%2C+F+H+Drummond&amp;rft.au=W+E+Agar%2C+F+H+Drummond&amp;rft.date=1948&amp;rft.volume=25&amp;rft.pages=103&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Lamarckism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFW_E_Agar.2C_F_H_Drummond.2C_M_M_Gunson1954">W E Agar, F H Drummond, M M Gunson (1954). "Fourth (final) report on a test of McDougall's Lamarckian experiment on the training of rats". <i>Journal of Experimental Biology</i> <b>31</b>: 308.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Fourth+%28final%29+report+on+a+test+of+McDougall%27s+Lamarckian+experiment+on+the+training+of+rats&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Experimental+Biology&amp;rft.aulast=W+E+Agar%2C+F+H+Drummond%2C+M+M+Gunson&amp;rft.au=W+E+Agar%2C+F+H+Drummond%2C+M+M+Gunson&amp;rft.date=1954&amp;rft.volume=31&amp;rft.pages=308&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Lamarckism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
