<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFDesmond1989">Desmond, Adrian (1989). <i>The Politics of Evolution: Morphology, Medicine, and Reform in Radical London</i>. Chicago: University of Chicago Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0226143740" class="internal">ISBN 0-226-14374-0</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Politics+of+Evolution%3A+Morphology%2C+Medicine%2C+and+Reform+in+Radical+London&amp;rft.aulast=Desmond&amp;rft.aufirst=Adrian&amp;rft.au=Desmond%2C+Adrian&amp;rft.date=1989&amp;rft.place=Chicago&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Chicago+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-226-14374-0&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Lamarckism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
